Washington, DC reports long-term-care data for Skilled Nursing facilities and Assisted-Living facilities. The Skilled Nursing Home data is cumulative since March 2020 and on December 10, 2020, DC added data for Assisted-Living Facilities. Resident and staff cases and deaths are reported separately. DC reports confirmed and probable cases separately for both residents and staff. Data is updated daily.
